Suite/Test/Step Name: TS001
Description: Data driven test for finding service centre around the several suburb names in the data files

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/TC002
Description:
Step 1-Navigate to given URL
Step 2-Search for given keyword
Step 3-Click on find location 
Step 4-Enter suburb name
Step 5-Filtered to only show service centre name
Step 6-Click one of service centre name

Suite/Test/Step Name: openBrowser("")
maximizeWindow()
navigateToUrl("https://www.service.nsw.gov.au/")
click(findTestObject("Service NSW Object/input_Service NSW makes it easier to find government information and services_q"))
setText(findTestObject("Service NSW Object/input_Service NSW makes it easier to find government information and services_q"), "Apply for a number plate")
click(findTestObject("Service NSW Object/button_apply for a number plate_button button--primary"))
scrollToElement(findTestObject("Service NSW Object/div_ 87 results found"), 0)
click(findTestObject("Service NSW Object/a_Apply for a number plate"))
click(findTestObject("Object Repository/Service NSW Object/a_Find locations"))
scrollToElement(findTestObject("Service NSW Object/div_ search by suburb"), 0)
setText(findTestObject("Object Repository/Service NSW Object/input_Search by suburb, postcode or current_d530bf"), suburb)
click(findTestObject("Object Repository/Service NSW Object/button_Sydney South 2000_button button--pri_c5c898"))
click(findTestObject("Object Repository/Service NSW Object/button_Service Centres"))
scrollToElement(findTestObject("Service NSW Object/h2_6 Service NSW locations"), 0)
